text: Martin Karlsson (born February 13, 1996) is a Swedish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Färjestad BK of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Karlsson made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Färjestad BK during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Färjestad BK players Category:Swedish ice hockey left wingers
